title: Dark County: A collection of four tales of terror.
description: Dark County isn't like other places in the midwest. Some say the dead reside here. This is a collection of those spine tingling tales. A nurse's fate, A baby's cry, a scortched youth and a tale of what happens when you mess with things you shouldn't and many more. Join me on this journey into Dark County.
author: J.L. Egly
